---
title: Southwestern-Inspired Chicken Tacos with Charred Corn and Tomato Salsa
description: These tacos pack a double whammy! We can’t decide what we like more: the tangy salsa or the incredible creamy Southwest-spiced pulled chicken! Luckily, you get the best of both in these warm tortillas.
